== Icelandic ==

=== Interjection ===

'''góðan daginn'''

# (colloquial) [[good day]]
# (colloquial) [[good morning]]

=== Usage notes===

Although this is uncorrect in a grammaritical sense ([[góða daginn]] or [[góðan dag]] should be used instead), very few icelanders know about that- so in a more colloquial sense it is correct.

